comments: Joseph (SAC) makes hand on ball contact during Booker's (PHX) upward shooting motion.
Hield (SAC) slightly extends his off arm to Booker's (PHX) front during his drive however, Booker (PHX) is able to defend through the contact.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Booker (PHX) and absorbs the contact.
Booker (PHX) does not fully establish legal position in Hield's (SAC) path following the hand off however, the contact created is marginal.
Hield (SAC) cleanly dislodges the ball during the hand off  between Booker (PHX) and Rubio (PHX).
As Joseph (SAC) and Baynes (PHX) engage during the rebound, Joseph (SAC) briefly grasps Baynes' (PHX) arm however, the contact is marginal.
As Hield (SAC) returns to the floor, his trailing arm makes contact with the ball during Booker's (PHX) upward shooting motion.
Booker (PHX) makes marginal contact to Barnes (SAC) as they disengage from the pick.
Baynes (PHX) makes contact Barnes' (SAC) wrist during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Baynes (PHX) makes contact to Holmes' (SAC) arm that affects his FOM during the rebound.
James (SAC) commits a take foul on Rubio (PHX).
Rubio (PHX) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Joseph (SAC) and absorbs the contact.
Bogdanovic (SAC) makes marginal contact to Oubre Jr.'s (PHX) after the release of the pass.
Booker (PHX) commits a take foul on Barnes (SAC).
Barnes (SAC) slightly extends his arm into Booker (PHX) as they release from the screen however the contact made is marginal.
Joseph (SAC) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
